narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Dubuque Internal Medicine PC is a Clinic/Center, End-Stage Renal Disease (ESRD) Treatment provider based in Platteville, WI. From 2021-01 through 2021-09, this provider received $115K in Medicaid payments across 2K claims serving 223 beneficiaries, billing 2 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: 100% of all billing comes from a single procedure code: 90999 (90999). This extreme concentration is unusual and may indicate specialized services or a narrow billing pattern.
Billing stopped in 2021-09, suggesting this provider is no longer active in Medicaid. Abrupt cessation of billing can be a risk indicator.
